OL,5, A collection of modern sonnets inspired
OL,6, by poet Hannah Lowe's decade teaching  
OL,7, in an inner London school has been     
OL,8, named the Costa Book of the Year.      
OL,10,FLowe's book The Kids was described as  
OL,11,F"a joy to read" by the chair of judges,
OL,12,FBBC journalist Reeta Chakrabarti.      
OL,14,FLowe has won #30,000 for her "poignant,
OL,15,Fwitty, thoughtful and universal" work. 
OL,17,FIts 66 sonnets convey the highs and    
OL,18,Flows of teaching A-level English, and  
OL,19,Foffer fictionalised portraits of some  
OL,20,Fof her adolescent students.            
